query:
update master_data 
        set 
            is_company = true
        from    (select replace(symbol_esignal_ticker,'/','-')  as symbol_esignal_ticker
                from 
                  nyse_instruments ni
                where 
                  instrument_type in (Select unnest($1::text[]))
                    and is_staged = false
                ) as r
        where 
            r.symbol_esignal_ticker = issue_symbol
